issues.description:
from [http://localhost:3001/measurements](http://localhost:3001/measurements) 

if we click in any of the Dates, we should be redirected to the edition of the data of that day.
However we are sent back to Home page.

f7e9f28c-6326-4556-8ff5-8d5eb0ec046b.body:
I'm ok with having a limit. It makes sense. We'll just have to mention it somewhere so users are not surprised. 

Perhaps doing 2 months would be less restrictive. Or just go with quarter. So within 3 months you have room even if you're backlogging workouts. But older than that stays uneditable. 

@diego88aku
